    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName><name ref="Ildibertus">Ildiperto</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie Rachiperti</persName> riceve da <persName
                            key="#Subdeacons"><name ref="Danihel">Danihel</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Andreas">Andree</name></persName> (…) livellario nomine ad
                        censum perxolvendum (…) idest quinque petiis de terris illis in loco ubi
                        dicitur Stanipagio prope <placeName ref="#places/489"
                        >Pontetecto</placeName>, pertenens <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/132"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Emperor/king #Churches #Subdeacons #vassusOf"
                            >Sancti Salvestri</orgName>, quas tu per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellum</rs> habis da <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #vassusOf" ref="#people/3313">Ghisalmari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king #vassusOf">vuasso domni imperatori</rs>, quas ego
                        ipse terre modo ad manus mea abere videor; et est <rs key="#Confinia"
                            >tenentes ipse una petia de terra uno caput</rs> in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, alio caput tenet in terra Gumperti, lato uno tenet in
                        terra Sancti Romani, alio lato tenet in terra Natali presbiteri; et ille
                        alia petia uno caput tenet in via publica, alio caput tenet in terra
                        Teudiprandi not, lato uno tenet in terra Sancte Marie, et alio latus tenet
                        in via publica; et ille tertia petia uno caput tenet in via publica, alio
                        caput tenet in terra Sancti Martini, lato uno tenet in terra Sancte Marie;
                        et ille quarta petia uno caput tenet in terra Teudi, lato uno tenet in
                        terraque fuit Teudilasci episcopi et alio latus tenet in terra de filii
                        quondam Balderichi; et illa quinta petia ambas capitas et ambas lateras
                        tenet in terra Sancti Martini; (…). Censo (pro omni censum et iustitia):
                        usque dum vos eas per ipsum libellum abueritis, per singulos annos in mense
                        martio (…) hic Luca ad casa abitationis vestre argentum denarios bonos
                        expendiviles numero sexaginta tantum (…) Pena: argentum soledos triginta
                        (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                                >Adalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: </ab>
                </div>
